  "keyFeatures": [
    "System-wide audio transcription via global hotkeys",
    "Three transcription modes: Standard, Push-to-Talk, and AI Assistant",
    "Groq API integration for fast, accurate AI transcription",
    "Smart text enhancement with auto-punctuation and phrase replacement",
    "WhisperKit support for optional local/offline transcription",
    "Customizable hotkey system with conflict detection",
    "Real-time recording overlay with visual and audio feedback",
    "Automatic clipboard copy and paste integration",
    "Hive-based local storage for privacy-first data handling",
    "Seamless auto-updates via Sparkle framework",
    "BLoC state management with Clean Architecture",
    "Light and dark theme support"
